headline.main: Capt. Eddie Rickenbacker Is Dead at 82; Rickenbacker, Ace of World War I, Is Dead Opposed to Interference B-17 Crash-Landed Took Engineering Course Attended Gunnery School

abstract: Capt Edward (Eddie) Rickenbacker, leading US mil aviator during World War 1 dies in Zurich, Switzerland on July 23; illus
snippet: Eldie Rickenbacker, a leading fighter ace in World War I and retired chairman of Eastern Air Lines, died early yesterday in a Zurich hospital.
